      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>chopped tomato</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>chopped red onion </strong>and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>red wine vinegar</strong></p><p>Add a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Stir it all together – this is your <strong>salsa criolla</strong></p>",
