    {
      "instruction": "<p>In a separate bowl, combine the<strong> chopped parsley </strong>with the<strong> chopped garlic </strong>(not a big garlic fan? try using less!), <strong>half </strong>your <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) (save the rest for another recipe!) and the <strong>remaining red wine vinegar</strong></p><p>Add 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]<strong> </span>olive oil</strong> with a pinch of<strong> sugar </strong>and <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>chimichurri</strong></p>",
